Package sait.bms.problemdomain

Class Paperback

java.lang.Object
sait.bms.problemdomain.Books
sait.bms.problemdomain.Paperback
public class Paperback
extends Books
This class is a subclass of the Books class, and contains unique attributes of authors, year and genre.
Author:
Nathan Ryan
